name: Climate Graph 001
description: Through over-dependence on fossil fuels, a subsequent runaway greenhouse effect, and deforestation for oil and agriculture, we are approaching terminal decline of delicate ecosystems that harbor more biodiversity in plants per hectare than entire continents. The ones who live and depend on these ecosystems for their livelihood are at the frontlines of protecting them. This NFT serves as a drop in the bucket to aid the frontlines of this struggle. Funds go to Amazon Frontlines. Data from GISS.
